| Suppression window definition | Defined in §6.7: step-basis or time-basis, configurable |
| `selected` audience resolution | Defined in §6.5: SelectedAudienceResolver interface registered by coordination |
| Connectivity-to-routing escalation interface | Defined in §7: RoutingEscalationHook; one-directional |
| Coordination-connectivity interaction boundary | Defined in §8: coordination calls connectivity; not vice versa |
